      "span_text": "since PC cell responses are tuned to high spatial frequencies and low temporal rate of flickering and the MC cells have the opposite response, i.e., they are tuned to low spatial frequencies and high temporal rates of flicker [CITATION_1] , we designed stimuli with variables in these two dimensions."
